Cell["\<\
Apparently, the CNOT gate \"copies\" the computational basis state of the \
first qubit to the second qubit.\
\>", "TechNoteMathCaption",
 CellID->1370698012,ExpressionUUID->"f1c67fff-7856-4cf5-89ee-40cf6b0dbbab"],

